{"tid":634204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【指新疆人權遭嚴重侵犯　美擬制裁中國官員】","createTime":"2018-04-19T04:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T11:39:18.000Z","uid":5195,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"39959ff3ae7f5493c9c19258fccfbf3a3ec57027","tid":634204,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"據美國傳媒消息，美國國務院代理助理國務卿史東（Laura Stone）指控中國拘留「成千上萬」（tens of thousands）的新疆維吾爾人和穆斯林，聲稱若有違反人權狀況，美國可能會根據《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》制裁中國官員。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，中共政府以「人民的反恐戰爭」(People&rsquo;s War on Terror)為名，嚴格限制新疆的宗教及文化活動，甚至大規模監視和任意拘捕維吾爾人及穆斯林，成千上萬的人已被關進拘留中心無限期被逼接受「政治教育」。<br />\n<br />\n除當地市民，有6名記者的家人遭到羈押，其中有4位美國公民、兩位美國永久居民，他們均為自由亞洲電台（Radio Free Asia）報道新疆消息，史東表示關注他們的狀況。"},{"pid":"db043b766a9c9ea0482aabcc4cf881a2b6bfd66e","tid":634204,"uid":83992,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n侵侵玩上癮"},{"pid":"39ea22f98a5df47ed172659e625e914d84a20ffb","tid":634204,"uid":55913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"喂 反擊呢？亮劍呢？"},{"pid":"67d6310d58a48084353075e913e4a155a94ce92b","tid":634204,"uid":122377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"中國比人食住上 <br />\n又唔敢還拖 有排受"},{"pid":"74c1e81a1c21934a11cb2acec325d676bd7227c1","tid":634204,"uid":40628,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"港人人權都被侵犯，快啲處理埋"},{"pid":"1b524d9bdbd706c587dd4afb2fd2595518d5853f","tid":634204,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c